{"title":"Detox \u0026 Immunity Boost","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eWe are all well aware of the role of the immune system in your life. The different flu seasons and winters come with infinite illnesses that put a question mark on your immunity. Is it that much able to tolerate disease? The daily increasing illnesses in your body can affect your whole body performance. Here, you need some immune-boosting solutions.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eNeuherbs range of Immunity \u0026amp; Wellbeing provides you with a complete solution for your immune system needs. Consisting of \u003cspan style=\"color: #167a62;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003evitamin C tablets\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e, herbal juices, \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.neuherbs.com\/products\/organic-apple-cider-vinegar-with-mother\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #167a62;\"\u003eApple cider vinegar\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e, Immunity boosting\u003cspan style=\"color: #167a62;\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.neuherbs.com\/products\/ashwagandha-1000-plus\" style=\"color: #167a62;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e Ashwagandha Tablets\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e, this immunity range can help you make your immune system fight fit with potent antioxidants and detoxifying. Herbs. These immune-boosting foods or supplements can be easily incorporated into your daily life routine to get you what your immune system wants.\u003c\/p\u003e","products":[{"product_id":"ashwagandha-1000-plus-tablets-stress-relief","title":"Ashwagandha 1000 Plus Tablets – Daily Lifestyle Support","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eneuherbs Ashwagandha 1000 Plus is made with natural ashwagandha root extract, Vitamin E, and B-complex (B6, B9, B12), along with piperine. This blend is designed to \u003cstrong data-start=\"1412\" data-end=\"1497\"\u003ehelp maintain balance, support an active lifestyle, and promote everyday wellness\u003c\/strong\u003e.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (60 Tablets)","offer_id":40975944614058,"sku":"NA1000P60","price":319.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"2 Months Pack - (120 Tablets)=Recommended","offer_id":41395707478186,"sku":"NA1000P60P2-1","price":598.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/ashwagandha_tablets_1000_plus_1.jpg?v=1754394534"},{"product_id":"organic-ashwagandha-powder-energy-stress-relief","title":"Ashwagandha Powder - Boost Energy, Reduce Stress","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003eAshwagandha is an evergreen Ayurvedic medicinal herb that’s been used for over 3000 years to promote health and wellbeing. Also referred to as the Indian Ginseng, Ashwagandha helps rejuvenate body and mind alike, manage stress, improve mood, induce calmness, increase stamina and energy levels, manage inflammation, and reduce oxidative stress. Ashwagandha helps manage insomnia, stress, anxiety, and promote calmness in mind \u0026amp; body. Ashwagandha also contains antioxidants that are known to improve immunity. Ashwagandha powders are designed to improve sleep quality and sleep cycle, relax the mind, and manage tiredness and general fatigue that’s associated with all day stress. neuherbs 100% pure \u0026amp; natural Ashwagandha Powder is made from the finest Ashwagandha root to access the maximum benefits of withanolides:the active ingredient of ashwagandha. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Pack of 1  - (100 GM)","offer_id":43426208776362,"sku":"NOASP100","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Pack of 2 - (100+100)GM","offer_id":45801787293866,"sku":"NOASP100P2","price":398.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Ashwagandha_powder_1_668accd6-0b57-4208-9f34-d349d5e07884.png?v=1766468142"},{"product_id":"organic-moringa-powder-immunity-weight-loss","title":"Moringa Powder for Immunity, Weight Loss, Gut Health","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003eMoringa are the leaves of a delicious vegetable drumstick. Also known as the miracle tree or ben oil tree, moringa is highly nutritious and loaded with antioxidants and anti-inflammatory properties. It is also rich in Vitamin A, C, and B complex, Calcium, Iron, Magnesium, and Dietary Fiber. Moringa leaves are low in fat and don’t contain bad cholesterol. Moringa leaf has a unique and delicious taste – popularly used in dals, sabjis, chapati dough, and smoothies etc. Moringa leaves offer a wealth of health benefits, ranging from enhancing immunity, supporting weight loss, promoting a healthy gut, to improving vision. Buy Moringa Leaf Powder, which is 100% preservative and additive-free, pure, and natural by neuherbs. The neuherbs moringa powder is also an excellent source of Amino acids and, therefore, is known to increase stamina, vitality, and energy levels. Consuming neuherbs Moringa Powder regularly can ensure better health and well-being, so grab now.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Starter Pack - (100 GM)","offer_id":43426143338666,"sku":"NOMRP100","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Saver Pack - (200GM)","offer_id":46309740642474,"sku":"NOMRP200","price":249.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Moringa_powder_1.webp?v=1762411648"},{"product_id":"spirulina-tablet","title":"Organically Spirulina Tablets for High Energy, Immunity and Weight Management for Men and Women","description":"\u003cp\u003eSpirulina is one of the most nutritionally dense substances known to man, with antioxidants, phytonutrients, probiotics, along with micro and macronutrients, alongside vitamins such as beta carotene, vitamin C, and vitamin E or minerals such as iron, calcium, chromium, copper, phosphorus, and potassium. Spirulina has several health benefits. We at neuherbs bring to you the goodness of spirulina, in a convenient tablet form, to help you avail its nutritional benefits whenever convenient, throughout the day. Thus, neuherbs Spirulina tablets made with 100% natural \u0026amp; Organic spirulina in tiny tablets compared to regular tablets thus are easy to incorporate into your daily routine and also do not contain any artificial additives which maintains its purity as well as safety. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Smart Pack - (120 Tablets)","offer_id":43954400493738,"sku":"NST120","price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Artboard_1_24027813.jpg?v=1763725053"},{"product_id":"moringa-tablet","title":"Organically Certified Moringa Tablet for High Energy, Detoxification and overall wellness for Men and Women","description":"\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\" class=\"sort-description\"\u003eneuherbs bring to you the goodness of Organic Moringa in the form of easy-to-use tablets that are enriched with essential nutrients to help you enjoy every day with full energy. Neuherbs Moringa Tablets are made from pure, natural organic moringa leaf powder without added preservatives, colour or any extra additives, which as per studies are a rich source of protein, vitamins, minerals, fiber \u0026amp; antioxidants. Organic Moringa tablets can be easily incorporated into daily lifestyles to obtain their natural health advantages including high energy, stronger immunity, body detoxification, reduced inflammation \u0026amp; holistic wellness. So, add this magical herb to your diet \u0026amp; avail yourself of several health benefits with it. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Smart Pack - (120 Tablets)","offer_id":43954501943466,"sku":"NMT120","price":299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/moringa_tablets_1.png?v=1754393627"},{"product_id":"true-calcium-plant-based-vitamin-d3","title":"True Calcium Tablets with Plant Vitamin D3 for Stronger Bones","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAn amazing 3-in-1 supplement for daily bone and muscle care, neuherbs True Calcium supplement by neuherbs contains 1000 mg of calcium in a more bioavailable Calcium Citrate form, more-bioavailable Vitamin D3, and natural Magnesium. All three vital nutrients work together to maintain strong bones, increase bone density, support muscle, tendon relaxation and contraction, reducing the risk of fractures and brittle bones later in life. True Calcium, the plant-based calcium tablets, help fill the daily calcium gap in adults. Paired with Vitamin D3 it supports better absorption of calcium in the body. Th unique combination of magnesium \u0026amp; calcium in these calcium tablets for bones works synergistically to support muscles contraction, relaxation \u0026amp; improve overall flexibility.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Monthly Pack - (60 Tablets)","offer_id":44271815033002,"sku":"NTC60","price":299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Saver Pack - (120 Tablets)","offer_id":46152267366570,"sku":"NTC60P2","price":598.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/true_calcium_tablets_1.png?v=1747133307"},{"product_id":"true-multivitamin-tablets-women-health","title":"True Vitamin Women: Multivitamin Tablets For Women","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated explicitly for adult women to help manage their daily nutritional needs. neuherbs True Vitamin Women multivitamin tablets contains 34 ingredients including four essential blends that provide comprehensive wellness support. The multivitamin tablets offer 100% RDA of essential vitamins with vital minerals, amino acids, and plant-based vitamin D3, which help women nourish and improve their bones, heart, immunity, and hair- skin effectively. These multivitamin tablets for women help manage hormonal balance, elevated mood and poor reproductive health. The amino acids with vitamin b complex help with fatigue and boost energy levels required to carry out daily tasks effectively.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (30 Tablets)","offer_id":44862088511658,"sku":"NTVW30","price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"2 Month Pack (Recommended) - (60 Tablets)","offer_id":46122548265130,"sku":"NTVW30P2","price":698.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/True_Multivitamin_women_1.jpg?v=1742446747"},{"product_id":"true-multivitamin-adult-40-plus-tablets","title":"True Multivitamin Adult 40+ Tablets - Immunity, Energy, Digestion","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eScientifically designed for men and women above 40 years of age, neuherbs True Multivitamin Adults 40+ tablet is made with 13 vitamins, 9 minerals and unique herbal blend essential for the body’s optimal functioning that naturally starts declining after 40. True multivitamin tablets offer great digestive benefits due to the presence of digestive enzymes \u0026amp;amp; probiotics content in it, helping you in smooth digestion, better nutrient absorption and happy mood as well. A natural blend of ginseng and L lysine may improve metabolism and overall energy levels considerably. Its herbal blend containing ayurvedic herbs like Brahmi and Bhringraj helps calm the mind, improve focus \u0026amp;amp; mental clarity. neuherbs True Multivitamin Adults 40+ is further enriched with plant-based Vitamin D3 to maintain healthy bones \u0026amp;amp; maximize well-being.\u