yes, does it get properly absorbed by your body? Do you still feel lethargic after eating healthy food? The answer to all these questions is fulfilment of daily nutritional needs with appropriate absorption. And it is not an easy task. But including a multivitamin into the daily diet can help. Neuherbs True Vitamin Daily multivitamin tablet is formulated with 22 key ingredients which are validated by science to provide various health benefits. Neuherbs Multivitamin is a solution for today’s unhealthy habits of binging on fast food that only offers empty calories \u0026amp; zero nutrition. We designed this formula of Multivitamin (Vitamin A, E, C, D \u0026amp; B complex) Multimineral (Zinc, Magnesium, Copper, Selenium,) along with ginseng and antioxidant from Grape Seed extract (95% Proanthocyanins) to help you provide overall strength, stamina, enhanced immunity, support heart, brain health and improve quality of life.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Monthly Pack - (30 Tablets)","offer_id":45186056913066,"sku":"NTV30","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/multivitamin_daily_1.webp?v=1770889233"},{"product_id":"natural-spirulina-powder-boost-energy-immunity","title":"Natural Spirulina Powder to boost Energy \u0026 Immunity","description":"\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIntroducing 100% natural \u0026amp; pure Spirulina Powder. Spirulina is a blue-green algae that contains a vast variety of essential vitamins, \u0026amp; minerals such as thiamin, niacin, riboflavin, copper, potassium, magnesium, and iron. It also contains omega 3,6 and protein, in small amounts. The protein in spirulina is considered excellent and delivers essential amino acids. Consuming spirulina powder every day can help reduce oxidative stress by fighting damage caused by free radicals, hence boost immunity. Consuming Spirulina Powder can be beneficial in reducing fatigue, increasing energy and enhancing endurance. So, consume neuherbs Spirulina Powder daily to boost your immunity \u0026amp; energy in one go. neuherbs Spirulina Powder is produced from pure and natural Spirulina, offering a nutritionally rich combination of vitamins, minerals, antioxidants, and protein.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Starter Pack- (100GM)","offer_id":45476472684714,"sku":"NSPP100","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/spirulina_powder_1.jpg?v=1747985894"}],"url":"https:\/\/neuherbs.com\/collections\/detox-immunity-wellbeing.oembed","provider":"Neuherbs","version":"1.0","type":"link"}